# Implementation Plan - Digital Plaid

Digital Plaid is a high-end, tactical Disney companion PWA designed for parents. It features a 2026-ready rule engine, offline-first resilience, and a sophisticated "Executive Plaid" design.

## Proposed Changes

### [Component] Project Setup

- [NEW] Initialize Expo (React Native) with TypeScript.
- [NEW] Integrate NativeWind for styling.
- [NEW] Setup Supabase for backend services (Auth, Database, Edge Functions).

### [Component] Data Layer

- [NEW] Refined Supabase Schema:
  - `trips`: [id](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/RiderSwitchProcessor.ts#3-41), `user_id`, `resort_id`, `start_date`, `end_date`, `goal`, `stamina_score` (1-10).
  - `guests`: [id](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/RiderSwitchProcessor.ts#3-41), `trip_id`, `name`, [age](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/OfflineStorage.ts#7-53), `gender`, `height_cm`, `sensory_sensitivities` (JSON).
  - `preferences`: `guest_id`, `item_id`, `item_type`, `rank`, `allergies`, `character_type_pref`, `snack_habit`, `already_done` (boolean).
  - `surveys`: [id](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/RiderSwitchProcessor.ts#3-41), `trip_id`, `guest_id`, `status` (Sent/Completed/LeaderFilled).
  - `itinerary_steps`: [id](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/RiderSwitchProcessor.ts#3-41), `trip_id`, `step_name`, `park_id`, `planned_start`, `actual_start`, `status`, `is_pivot`, `nudge_id`.
  - `memory_logs`: [id](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/RiderSwitchProcessor.ts#3-41), `trip_id`, `log_date`, `planned_v_actual`, `sentiment_score`, `memory_note`, `nudge_log` (JSON).

### [Component] Logic Engines

- [NEW] [2026RuleEngine.ts](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/2026RuleEngine.ts):
  - **Dynamic Rule Switching**: WDW/DL logic.
  - **Pathing Penalty**: +20 min crossing penalty for parades/fireworks.
  - **Refurbishments**: Hard-coded exclusions.
- [NEW] [Recalibrator.ts](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/Recalibrator.ts):
  - **The Brain**: Triggers on `Down` or `>20min` spikes.
  - **Comfort Logic**: Time-aware pivots (1-4 PM) for AC/indoor shows.
  - **Proximity Search**: Finds Like-to-Do/Characters < 20 min wait.
- [NEW] [TacticalCoach.ts](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/TacticalCoach.ts):
  - **Persona Identity**: Narrative [Pivot] + [Data] + [Benefit] structure.
  - **Hanger Watchdog**: 3-hour gap detection for snack nudges.
  - **Rider Switch Tone**: Logistical empathy for the waiting parent.
- [NEW] [MemoryRecapScreen.tsx](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/screens/MemoryRecapScreen.tsx):
  - **Comparison Timeline**: Vertical side-by-side (Original vs. Actual).
  - **Joy Sparkline**: SVG-based chart mapping sentiment.
  - **Wins Header**: Dynamic calculation of minutes saved.
- [NEW] [BatteryStrategist.ts](file:///Users/patchenuchiyama/Documents/digital-plaid/src/utils/BatteryStrategist.ts):
  - **Ultra-Light Mode**: Activates < 20% battery. Kill non-essential fetches.
  - **Lazy Fetching**: Event-driven data pings.

